NIEHS Simulation Data
For our example of estimating the effects of simultaneous interventions on multiple variables, we will use simulated data from the 2015 NIEHS Mixtures Workshop. The data has already been loaded into R in the background as assigned to the object mixtures, but you can view and download the raw data here.

