\(\bar{X}_t = (X_1, ..., X_t)\)
The history of a variable up until time \(t\)


\(\underline{X}_t = (X_t, ..., X_\tau)\)
The future of a variable, including time \(t\)


\(H_t = (\bar{A}_{t-1}, \bar{L}_t)\)
The history of all variables up until just before \(A_t\)


